channel.title: Dev Console Glitch?
channel.description:
Now this could be nothing and i may be an idiot but i logged onto rs for the first time in months and hit something and this came up on my screen.
[img]http://img12.imageshack.us/img12/2349/picture6zga.png[/img]
The developers console? I'm guessing that normal players aren't supposed to see this because it says the build number in the corner and is...the developers console. As you can see I typed some moparscape commands in to it as a joke but could this be useful in any way?

item.title: Dev Console Glitch?
item.dc:creator: @Metho_D Method
item.description:
@Metho_D wrote:

Normal players are supposed to see it, but have limited access. See this page for more about it.
